<TEXT>
Coca-Cola Amatil, the Australia-based soft drinks company which is
controlled by Coca-Cola of the US but is also listed on the Australian Stock
Exchange, yesterday reported a 45 per cent rise in profits after tax but
before abnormals, to ADollars 95.4m (USDollars 68.5m), writes Nikki Tait. In
